members.signatureBeforeChange: int windowProc (int hwnd, int msg, int wParam, int lParam)
members.signatureAfterChange: int windowProc (int hwnd, int msg, int wParam, int lParam)
diff: +					* Bug in Windows.  On XP, when a tooltip is hidden
+					* due to a time out or mouse press, the tooltip
+					* remains active although no longer visible and
+					* won't show again until another tooltip becomes
+					* active.  The fix is to reset the tooltip bounds.
